        <!-- College Intro -->
        <section class="college-intro">
            <div class="college-intro-content">
                <h2>Welcome to Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College</h2>
                <p>Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College is managed by Maa Maturani Devi Shikshan Sansthan. The College was established in the year 2018 to provide quality education in the field of health sciences. The trustees of the college are already serving the community through other colleges in Ballia. With an aim to promote quality education in pharmaceutical sciences and to fulfil the healthcare needs of society, the institution stands as a beacon of excellence.</p>
                <p>The college is recognized by AICTE, PCI New Delhi &amp; Board of Technical Education Uttar Pradesh. It offers two-year diploma programs (D.Pharma) and four-year degree programs (B.Pharma) in Pharmacy, designed to equip students with the knowledge and skills required to excel in the pharmaceutical care sector.</p>
                <p>Situated in the natural ambience of lush green fields and mango trees, the college provides an ideal environment for learning. The campus is fully equipped and independently housed, making it one of the most envied and suited locations for an educational institution in Ballia City.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="college-intro-image">
                <img src="/images/image.png" alt="College Campus" />
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Founder -->
        <section class="founder-wrapper">
            <div class="founder-title-section">
                <h1>Meet Our Founder</h1>
                <p>The visionary behind Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College</p>
            </div>
            <div class="founder-card-enhanced">
                <div class="founder-image-wrapper">
                    <img src="/images/image1.png" alt="Mr. Kedar Nath Verma - Founder" />
                </div>
                <div class="founder-content-enhanced">
                    <h2>Mr. Kedar Nath Verma</h2>
                    <div class="founder-title">Founder, Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College</div>
                    <p>A visionary leader with a deep commitment to education and community development, Mr. Kedar Nath Verma established Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College in 2018 with a mission to provide quality pharmaceutical education to aspiring students. His dedication to excellence and belief in holistic development have shaped the institution into a premier pharmacy college in the region.</p>
                    <p>With decades of experience in the education sector, he has successfully created an environment where students can thrive academically while developing strong ethical values. His vision is to create skilled, knowledgeable, and professional pharmacists who can serve the healthcare needs of society with compassion and competence.</p>
                    <div class="founder-quote-enhanced">
                        <i class="fas fa-quote-left"></i> "Education is not just about acquiring knowledge; it's about shaping character and building a better future. At Maa Maturani Devi Pharmacy College, we are committed to nurturing young minds to become responsible professionals who contribute meaningfully to society."
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

