        <!-- Vision & Mission -->
        <section class="college-intro vision-mission">
            <h2>Our Vision &amp; Mission</h2>
            <p><strong>Vision:</strong> To become a "Centre of Excellence" by providing quality and research-oriented Pharmacy education to meet industry, community, and stakeholder needs through continuous up-gradation.</p>
            <p><strong>Mission:</strong> To create ethical, knowledgeable, and professional pharmacists who serve healthcare needs with compassion and competence.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><strong>Our Commitment:</strong> The college is nestled in lush green surroundings, providing an ideal environment for learning. We nurture talent, encourage innovation, and produce skilled professionals ready for global challenges.</p>
